A method for buying bitcoins using cash through various methods including deposit at a bank (U.S.) or through Moneygram and Western Union.

##Methods of Payment

At the time of ZIGGAP's launch, the payment methods that show will very based on location (determined via IP address).

###U.S.

* Cash deposit (Chase Bank, PNC Bank)

###Australia

* Cash deposit (National Australia Bank/NAB)
* Online bill payment ([POLi payments](http://www.polipayments.com/consumer))

###Worldwide

* Moneygram
* Western Union

##History

ZIGGAP's launch was announced on January 29, 2013 (6.1).

